{"tid":284430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你個好朋友個女朋友唔太妥你...有無計?","createTime":"2017-06-15T02:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T03:21:37.000Z","uid":114421,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c79ac9ec2a749e25d212467c4479fd5e982bc848","tid":284430,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:14:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的...<br />\n我有個識左10年既好朋友一直以黎都好close, 因為大家都喺外國讀書, 同中學, 同大學之後仲一齊租屋住所以一個星期可能有8成既時間都會一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年黎都無野 但條友最近同左個女仔一齊就開始黎料...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重色輕友我明, 個個人都係嫁啦, 但我發現原來係個女仔唔太鐘意我<br />\n其實我都拗哂頭, 我自問對個女仔都幾好<br />\n幫佢呢樣果樣, 我個friend唔得閒時佢有需要我又會車佢, 但就唔明佢唔鐘意我啲乜???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂大佬, 你唔鐘意我其實無乜野, 但你每一日每一分每一秒都同我個friend一齊搞到打牌又無佢, 食飯又無佢, 最慘係睇波你都唔比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而加唔係我識少你呢個朋友就算, 係我無左個識左10年既好朋友呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話我係女既你都仲可以有得講呀, 頂我男人黎嫁!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於點解我會話個女仔唔太鐘意我, 因為佢講野勁大聲比我聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad3c42234715f9d7184453f948beac79079e1ec","tid":284430,"uid":15486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:17:03.000Z","msg":"你有冇叫你個fd幫手問下點解"},{"pid":"f5e29042f5902876845c147e40432c91dd21243c","tid":284430,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"下次車佢去荒山野嶺掉低佢"},{"pid":"12329364c494fcfcdb2b182c39ac0c339aaa7fa9","tid":284430,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次車佢去荒山野嶺掉<span style=\"color: red;\">鑊</span>佢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a7d87358d0268c4451fa1b2d7b719303ebf7c1d3","tid":284430,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有冇叫你個fd幫手問下點解</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有, &quot;你諗多左啦&quot;, &quot;佢講啫&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d1760874701e56d6d9dac388faf1de68596d58","tid":284430,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下次車佢去荒山野嶺掉<span style=\"color: red;\">鑊</span>佢</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點樣&quot;掉鑊&quot;佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0a9d7eadb7926a85f530fcc6d1175ccab0c91d","tid":284430,"uid":61075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fdf097f4d99a7aa0c50ef2578e6a3caeb4817c","tid":284430,"uid":97465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"用條撚塞住佢個口"},{"pid":"eaf0a99d490bd70d6dde3abbcb35735c39a245b6","tid":284430,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-